snippet.title: Edge of Eternity - Chapter 3 Release date teaser
snippet.description:
The third chapter of Edge of Eternity, enthralling JRPG adventure from indie team Midgar Studio will be available for free on July 17 on Steam!

For the latest news about Edge of Eternity, don't forget to follow us on social media:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EoeGame/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/EoeGame
Discord: https://discord.gg/EoEgame

Please take the time to wishlist us on Steam if you're interested in the game:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/269190/Edge_Of_Eternity/

You can also follow our publisher Dear Villagers for more Edge of Eternity news:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DearVillagers/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/dearvillagers
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dearvillagers/
